    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一张完整的Laravel生产环境架构图。先从客户端层开始吧，有三种入口：浏览器、移动端App，还有外部API调用方。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Browser",
        "MobileApp",
        "ExternalAPI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，这三类客户端都归到Client Layer子图里。接下来它们应该统一走到负载均衡层？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client Layer",
        "Load Balancing"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，中间要加一个Load Balancer，所有流量先过它。然后分发到三个Web Server，我们都用FrankenPHP加Laravel Octane。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LB",
        "WebServer1",
        "WebServer2",
        "WebServer3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，Application Layer子图里放了三个Web Server，标注了技术栈。现在画数据层？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Application Layer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "数据层比较复杂。主库用PostgreSQL，必须配一个只读副本做查询分流。另外Redis既当缓存又当队列驱动。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PrimaryDB",
        "ReadReplica",
        "Redis"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，Web Server是同时连PrimaryDB和ReadReplica吗？还是读写分离的逻辑？",
